Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝茶嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在有點忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放你門外了啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leaving it outside your door, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在你只需等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都會水到渠成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything's going to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓我會做好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I promised I'd make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐好啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶  看看我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Christ, would you look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在看你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高端專業人士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Top-end professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  你討厭你的手提箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, God, you hate your briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是對的  不用給我面子  太不搭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You do, it's fine, it's completely the wrong thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我留著發票呢  會退回去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've kept the receipt, I'll take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love it, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我討厭被人通知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's just that if someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在二十八歲生日當天要去上數據管理課\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd be spending my 28th birthday on a data management course...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  因為他們發現了你的潛質\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, cos they spotted your potential, is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是他們注意到我眼中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, or they noticed the last glimmer of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一線希望消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}disappear from my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可能要高升你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're probably grooming you for a big promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換我就會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓你做地區經理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd make you regional manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地區經理都做些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And what does a regional manager do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使喚別人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bosses people about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會喜歡的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You wouldn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到我的鞋了嗎  海莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you seen my shoes, Haley?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟其他鞋一起在鞋柜里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're in the shoe cupboard. With the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦子跟篩子似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brain like a sieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這家里可不能亂放東西啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't leave anything down in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫系統整理  弗雷迪  你也該試試\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's called a system, Freddie, you should give it a go some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會寫在待辦事項里的  埃米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I tell you what, put it on my to-do list, Amir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們今天是安排你去搭圍欄嗎  弗雷迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, have they got you on the fence today, Freddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧  至少是室外的活兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Probably. At least it's outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡跟那么多僵尸擠在一塊兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't fancy being cooped up with that rotter crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  你跟他們完全不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, you'd have nothing in common with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好豐盛的早餐啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Posh breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that in aid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會六點到家  把牛排煎上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll be home by six and I'll get the steaks on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家過生日真的沒事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you sure you're OK with a night in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別聽她的  埃米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't listen to her, Amir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們分開前  她生日我們總會出去慶祝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When we were married, we always went out on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次我們把自制雞尾酒點了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That time we nearly burnt down the Legion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點把軍團酒吧燒成平地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}setting those made-up cocktails on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有去惠特比旅行  這才叫過生日嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Whitby. Now, That was a birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}英國海濱小城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過我們沒能去到惠特比  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only we never got as far as Whitby, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們因為行為不檢點被趕下了火車\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got kicked off the coach for lewd behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那年在加里媽媽家  沒有泳池的泳池派對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Gary's mum's place that year. The pool party with no pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多美好的夜晚  你穿著那身比基尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What a night! And you in that bikini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又脫了那身比基尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you out of that bikini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是在回憶往事  跟你無關\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're only reminiscing. You've done all right out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總不能連回憶都不許我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't begrudge a bloke a few fond memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我受不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No...I'm not having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Amir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我做什么了  -夠了  我認真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What am I doing? - It's enough now. I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你會跟他說的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said you'd say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧  那我說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fine, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到  弗雷迪  抱歉  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Time's up, Freddie. Yeah, sorry, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從治療中心回來時  我們說好你住兩個月的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two months we said when you came back from the treatment centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天是八月九號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}August 9th that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是十二月六號  也是海莉的生日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}December 6th today. Haley's birthday, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I-I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們再給他一點時間  等他把車賣了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How about we just give him until he's sold the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之后再補你禮物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll give you a present later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每次跟你說這件事  你都這么說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every time I talk to you about it, it's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得內疚  他還沒準備好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You feel guilty, he's not ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他得把車賣了才能有一點存款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he's got to sell that bloody car to get a deposit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他根本就沒把車拿去掛牌出售  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not even put the car on the market, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海莉  你到底想不想讓他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Haley? Haley...do you want him gone or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Amir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要上班嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Working today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要這么叫的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If that's what you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你有些疑慮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you've had your misgivings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了些調查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I've been doing some research
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許多少能幫你釋惑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think may allay them somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查新鮮事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can always trust the lunatic fringe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總要靠狂熱分子  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to run down the new thing, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是壓迫  沒用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it's oppression, it'll never work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}從半死癥患者到總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人呢  你覺得她看著像受壓迫的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about her? Does she look oppressed to you?
