Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那晚看到了什么  桑德拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did you see that night, Sandra?
