Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克萊夫也是  難以置信吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So was Clive, would you believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從頭到尾都在睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Slept through the whole thing.
