Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且非常親密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In very close conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yeah.
