Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
