Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下流的禽獸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Filthy animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是開始也是結束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are the first and the last.
