Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他在哪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.56,0:26:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪  小潔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is he, Jem?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.51,0:26:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和埃米之間沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Things OK with you and Amir, then, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.75,0:26:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, no, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.34,0:26:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他上班時給我打了電話  都說清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he called me at work, so that's all sorted now.
