Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.13,0:26:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地方讓你想起點什么沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ringing any bells for you, this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.48,0:26:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.83,0:26:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你那天太醉記不住呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you might have been too off your face to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.15,0:27:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽會在那里升起來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The sun would have come up just about there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.69,0:27:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上就快要日出了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nearly did it the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.79,0:27:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我又想  我在干什么  就要日出了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then I thought, "What am I doing? It's got to be sunrise."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.28,0:27:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確實知道找場合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you do have a sense of occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.78,0:27:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我單膝跪下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Got on one knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.91,0:27:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你就是四肢著地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looked more like all fours from where I was standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.77,0:27:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那時也醉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bit worse for wear, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.34,0:27:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說了愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.28,0:27:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你戴上我的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put my ring on your finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.15,0:27:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那枚戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.43,0:27:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啤酒罐拉環做的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A ring-pull off an old beer can.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.72,0:27:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那是什么  你個土鱉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what it was, you cheap sod!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.94,0:27:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did the job, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.83,0:27:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成了世界上最幸福的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Made me the happiest man on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天  我那時好幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God, I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.64,0:27:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就應該是那樣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what it's supposed to be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.95,0:27:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還能重來  小海\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It could be again, Hales.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.11,0:27:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.23,0:27:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.37,0:27:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.63,0:28:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該解釋一下...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.63,0:28:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰去哪里工作不是我能決定的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I've no influence over who goes where.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.59,0:28:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是完全隨機的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's an entirely randomised process.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那個披頭散發男\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and the straggly-haired one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.55,0:28:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早早起來就在紙上寫名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}get up early to write names on a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.60,0:28:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你可以在我不在的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What I thought was that you could manage the phones
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.91,0:28:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接電話登記留言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and possibly take messages whilst I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.20,0:28:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你從帽子里抽出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then you pick them out of a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.66,0:28:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一遇到你  我就發現...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because when we met, I noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.82,0:28:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們相遇之時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our meeting, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.66,0:28:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個聰明有教養的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...that you're an intelligent and educated person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.52,0:28:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你應該\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I thought you might
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.11,0:28:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡在能施展才干的地方工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like to be somewhere you can exploit those skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不是完全隨機的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So not entirely randomised?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.02,0:28:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟秘書差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's like secretarial.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.76,0:28:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想我做你的秘書嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want me to be your secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.49,0:28:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人助理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Personal assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.65,0:28:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該喜歡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You might like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.18,0:28:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.83,0:28:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟你一起待在這里  我想和我朋友一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't like being here with you. I'd rather be with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.55,0:29:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  這邊來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.51,0:29:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你真準備這樣做嗎  -來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You really going to do this? - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.01,0:29:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用控制棍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Use the guiding stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.27,0:29:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.02,0:29:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照這個速度  我們得耗一整天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be here all day at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.54,0:29:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著這個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.62,0:29:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后扣在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you pop it on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.87,0:29:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后拉他們  過來  過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then you guide them. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.45,0:29:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來拿著啊  這又不是我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take it, then. It's not my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.88,0:29:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're just confusing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.07,0:29:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得用力拉扯它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You need to give it a good old yank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.23,0:29:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.41,0:29:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.30,0:29:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行  我們接手了  謝謝你  蒂尼絲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right, we'll take it from here. Thanks, Denise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.72,0:29:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.61,0:29:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會告訴羅素醫生她虐待他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll tell Dr. Russo she's mistreating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.68,0:29:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為羅素醫生面善  就會好心嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think Russo's any better just cos he gives you a smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:29:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅素也做不了什么  他也是棋子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Russo ain't going to do anything. He's part of the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.78,0:30:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也是  我們都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Same as she is. Same as we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.74,0:30:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果進展順利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we go along with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.00,0:30:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能弄他們出去  在小屋里治好他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we can get 'em out of here, medicate them back at the bungalow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.69,0:30:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不知道怎么照顧他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't know the first thing about looking after 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.18,0:30:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可能會發生意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anything could happen to 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.40,0:30:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管  他們不會待在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't care. They'll be out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.41,0:30:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們幾天后就去治療中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll be in the treatment centre in a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.19,0:30:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是安置他們的最佳地點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's the best place for 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.79,0:30:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為治療中心就能好些嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think things are better in the treatment centre?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.05,0:30:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂  你根本不了解那地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have no idea. You know nothing about that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.97,0:30:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  我不像你還對這些人盲目期待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I don't share your faith in these people being nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.22,0:30:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的  當你逐漸了解他們...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Really, when you get to know them...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.65,0:30:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會發現他們很殘忍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.86,0:30:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想參與進來  別做傻事  行嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want to be a part of it. Don't do anything stupid, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.75,0:30:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.51,0:30:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.68,0:31:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這里干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.99,0:31:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.29,0:31:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What with?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.99,0:31:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看看尸體在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Show me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.64,0:31:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴她了  加里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told her, Gaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.67,0:31:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠...小潔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, for f... Jem!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.44,0:31:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒得選\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had to.
