Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.03,0:36:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會跟你同流合污的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am not going to go along with you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.89,0:36:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把鑰匙放回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now put the keys back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.07,0:37:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再掉的就是你的腦袋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll forget your head next.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.93,0:37:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我一開始就看錯你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was wrong about you from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.98,0:37:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-等等  -我跟你這種人沒話說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Look... - I've got nothing to say to people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.68,0:37:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你有點膽量  我想錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought there was something there. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.88,0:38:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.70,0:38:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.29,0:38:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被選區的事耽擱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Held up by constituency business.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.88,0:38:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.89,0:38:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個十幾歲的男孩貌似失蹤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A teenage boy seems to have gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.27,0:38:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的一個鄰居  亨利·蘭思德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A neighbour of mine, actually. Henry Lonsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.65,0:38:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他昨晚沒回家  -半死患者還是活人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He didn't come home last night. - PDS or living?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.61,0:38:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半死患者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}PDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.06,0:38:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.85,0:38:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他母親挺擔心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His mother's quite upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.15,0:38:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她說如果明天還沒消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told her that we'd start circulating these
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就會發放尋人啟事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if there's still no sign by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.69,0:38:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.48,0:38:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也許能派上些用場呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought she could be of some use.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.05,0:39:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不這么做  讓她走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't do that. Get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.82,0:39:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.98,0:39:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.74,0:39:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去會會你的這位鄰居吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, then. Let's go and see this neighbour of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.41,0:39:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭思德太太  我向您保證\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Lonsdale, I wanted to reassure you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.09,0:39:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經盡全力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that everything is being done
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.92,0:39:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找亨利了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to locate Henry's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.34,0:39:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小冊子上說  幾小時不服藥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pamphlet says medication can wear off
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.00,0:39:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藥效就會消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}within hours of a missed dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.65,0:39:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在都快一整天了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been almost a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.36,0:39:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般這種情況  最后都發現其實\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very often in cases like this, the young person will turn out
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.05,0:39:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一直都待在朋友家呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to have been at a friend's house all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.94,0:39:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我沒問他的朋友嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you not think I've checked with his friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.04,0:39:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是夜宿朋友家了  菲利普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not on a sleepover, Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.82,0:39:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們知道亨利的想法和興趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What might be useful is if we had an idea of Henry's thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.75,0:39:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.17,0:39:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這能幫你們找到他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that helps find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.57,0:39:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常都很有幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Often.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.91,0:39:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很受歡迎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's very likeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.91,0:39:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他長得很精神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.08,0:40:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利跟你談過復生的經歷嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did Henry ever talk to you about the Rising?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.82,0:40:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有什么關系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's that got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.51,0:40:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想排除一些可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We want to eliminate certain lines of inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.06,0:40:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些更極端的半死神話傳說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a mythology amongst the more extreme PDS elements
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.75,0:40:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為第一批復生的人很特殊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the first risen is in some way special,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.24,0:40:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以應當有第二次復生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that they're needed to bring about a second Rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.10,0:40:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利就很特殊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Henry's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.07,0:40:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么個特殊法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.33,0:40:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有通靈能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.21,0:40:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復生后就有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Had 'em since he came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.73,0:40:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不承認  但能看出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He denied it but you could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.58,0:40:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時眼神迷離  我跟你說過的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Far-away look'd come over him. I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.07,0:40:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他提到過復生那晚看到什么了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did he talk about what he saw the night he rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.16,0:40:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本都是腳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, feet, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.80,0:40:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復生的時候各種走過他墓的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People walking over his grave as he was coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.47,0:40:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人  他不喜歡這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other ones. Didn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.34,0:40:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常在意自己的獨立空間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Always very protective of his personal space.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.06,0:40:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說他被綁架了  你還不以為然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said he were kidnapped. You pooh-poohed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.76,0:40:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被綁架的可能不大  但他很可能是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kidnapping is highly unlikely. He may, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.25,0:40:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一些極端分子有另類關系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have become involved with extremists by some other means.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.03,0:40:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須考慮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will have to look into
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.80,0:40:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利被一些極端分子招募\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the possibility that Henry was recruited
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.73,0:40:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并參加了他們的集訓營的可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and made his way to one of their training camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.76,0:41:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}今晚就走  車庫等你  弗雷迪  吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.01,0:41:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小壽星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, birthday girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.53,0:41:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的事不能再發生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing like that can happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.69,0:41:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我就喜歡大早上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And there was me looking forward to the next morning
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.47,0:41:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去森林里肢解尸體似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could spend cutting up a body in a wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.86,0:41:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了就再來一杯  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Another one of these when you're ready. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.60,0:41:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想做什么危害你事業的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Still, I don't want to do anything that might damage your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.30,0:41:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.60,0:41:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們那些政客不都一樣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the same, you politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.02,0:41:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在意這些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not what I'm concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.86,0:42:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維生黨在糾集小團體\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Victus has been gathering intelligence on groups
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.40,0:42:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算帶來二次復生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}looking to bring about another Rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.69,0:42:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們認為需要先找到第一個復生的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They believe they need to find the first risen before it can start.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.95,0:42:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要在諾頓村找\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're going to be looking in Roarton.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.03,0:42:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nut jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.75,0:42:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管第一個復生的是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whoever this first risen is,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.79,0:42:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須在其他人之前找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we want to find them before anyone else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.65,0:42:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事必須被阻止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It needs to be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.32,0:42:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來蘭思德家的男孩應該不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, as it turns out, this Lonsdale boy wasn't significant,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.49,0:42:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們也不能輕易冒這樣的險\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it's not the kind of risk we can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.31,0:42:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道這有多重要了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see how important this is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.72,0:42:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.41,0:42:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天去診所了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I went down to the GP surgery today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.04,0:42:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有兩個狂暴態僵尸被鎖在籠子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had two rabids there, locked up in a cage,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.09,0:42:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們將要送他們去治療\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that they're going to send away for treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.93,0:42:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去教育他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so that they can teach them...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.66,0:42:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使他們能夠滿足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to integrate, to be what the...
